This directory contains a vendored and modified copy of scrapion
(https://github.com/aula-id/scrapion), licensed under the Apache License 2.0.
See LICENSE for the full license text.

Modifications made for koma:
- Package renamed from `scrapion` to `scrapion_agent`
- All intra-package imports converted to relative imports
- Added `__main__.py` entrypoint for headless one-shot invocation via
  `python -m scrapion_agent --json "<query>"`
- Removed pyvirtualdisplay dependency (Display code was already commented out
  in the original; the dependency is omitted from requirements.txt)
- Firefox auto-install suppressed at runtime (koma --install-internet handles
  provisioning separately via SCRAPION_SKIP_BROWSER_CHECK=1)
